{"id": "art-217", "label": "Art. 217", "title": "Art. 217", "slug": "art-217", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 217 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_157617525\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1919\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_157617525\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dreptul de <span class=SpellE>preferin&#355;&#259;</span>\nal <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> poate fi limitat sau ridicat\nnumai prin hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale extraordinare a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1815211713\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1918\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1815211713\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, va pune la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ie</span>\nadun&#259;rii generale extraordinare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nun raport scris, prin care se precizeaz&#259; motivele limit&#259;rii sau\nridic&#259;rii dreptului de <span class=SpellE>preferin&#355;&#259;</span>.\nAcest raport va explica, de asemenea, modul de determinare a valorii de\nemisiune a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1230919083\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1917\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1230919083\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Hot&#259;rârea va fi luat&#259; în <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;a</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> reprezentând trei p&#259;trimi din\ncapitalul social subscris, cu majoritatea voturilor <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_200836918\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1916\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_200836918\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Hot&#259;rârea va fi depus&#259; la oficiul registrului <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> de c&#259;tre consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv de c&#259;tre directorat,\nspre <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionare</span> în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> publicare în Monitorul Oficial al României,\nPartea a IV-a.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}